Install:

  go install patel.codes/wiki@latest

Set up:

  $WIKI_CACHE_DIR should contain two bz2 downloads
  from Wikipedia.

  See: https://dumps.wikimedia.org/enwiki/20260501

  ```
  % la -h ~/d/wiki
  total 26G
  drwxr-xr-x  2 neal neal 4.0K May 30 23:34 .
  drwxr-xr-x 13 neal neal 4.0K May 30 19:00 ..
  -rw-r--r--  1 neal neal 269M May  6 00:28 enwiki-20260501-pages-articles-multistream-index.txt.bz2
  -rw-r--r--  1 neal neal  25G May  6 02:07 enwiki-20260501-pages-articles-multistream.xml.bz2
  ```
